Doom:Source E1M1-2

By XanderK9 (AkA Kain_Nine)
(takaro10 AT hotmail.com)

This map is based from the first and second levels of
the classic game: Doom.

Note: there is some places in the map that are very
dark, so the use of the flashlight or/and nightvision
googles are recommended. Also, this map feature random
respawns for both teams, so be prepared...

Enjoy! :)
